title.narrative: Information technology, supply, logistics and administration to effectively support country operations.

description.narrative: Operations continued to provide support to programme delivery with US$120 million in procurement, plus USD350 million in Procurement Services (including COVAX). A total of 151 long-term agreements (LTA) are in place to increase efficiency. HACT Assurance Activities were achieved with 16 audits completed which were pending from previous years. Minimum spot-checks were completed with introduction of outsourced physical spot checks by external chartered accountants. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2021
